[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Investigating JS resources**\n\nI'm considering how we can enhance our coverage by reading existing resources without adding dependencies. It seems we need to look into how the Closure third-party JavaScript resources are utilized with ClojureScript and the Closure Compiler. Perhaps we should check out the google-closure-library as it's often paired with org.clojure:google-closure-library. However, there's an issue with our Java runs failing for tests that were generated for the latest versions applied to older setups. I think we should inspect the old tests to clarify our next steps.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0dc7fb724c3e1eb2016a3e585905f881908cc1ce6a70cfb6d5\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqPlheLm8QTy2fpKy2MV_DL7h0JKY6O5K1zEOu6g2CoPQ5OIvW6xiFG3SQERUFtBxpTD1URTEozFgR_l9ewi2LEZWRHoOB8dXNvb-6w43uS1g1zTVLqNEuYlo5cGLH6H603J43kOsoig20FlavPSZ6_-UqsQ_WwOyPSrr2eZ-TqWS-Lp-FuaxEfFKNHr0XzLsMphLFws4mLiCb3CHSChneBtxcpvaTyio9RwmDfQ72eFFDDsW6Ibn9XVVoeBAxgNhn12Q6Jugc4whKDZS43Wptym_M3nvuhjd8nRAlFrX10bi0XZO_aSkhn581DVoCHGj7gLJ3RTAfHnVcL8tcP0mtZWXrGLiaEzy8pRlvH-je3_jYwKkXWrEUvN3D1KwMyvotSnWjApzSRSyIDxsi5N5I_Zb02_FlaCMJtKBuo9V1vfRqs6dsuBcMdQsHfuabsOz_UFbNeQIkZKbss_w7hR7ZpRqytj2VdIYyk4iF8t0cGW9nXiQxHMv2WQpPnO9O2p--1P9PWA1IejMfK-WRocjb7-zwz1v1hBRDq1APwgklp0d-AFcHLVQp44TmHPqC4QLqBZpw2pKDkpiqlCIbbx7bvfigceZ9Lq-uEss-eUZzez037mJrKvUzZjO9xpKstdW4OhlRco98dzM046JEpqLo7cvQQ2Aa9WrHnW-92xB8QHI8rliHZIUqd_nGExnB1u4KIup6pQzEmJlGHxstfYxIDxt9qEEOTbe4YD4uhgP0UCKwjBXBJFFcQoCWENndf1PgyTyy9NxVtwowp6sSOtzgw5N2A6maACgbdXDtb5gXspry3oMzT8l3lG0ODKCq6atz-P6-U0CqwuETrn8yfUmb1aodglpLSDFMNufN1yUUQ_D7XSj7eGm81KzIbC9ugUJvf1nMutD3EzdWwQNFM-AMA82YW3n-0ZBBNaIiaXw0d4_x5rkWU65iLCg5NO_6Y3hAyj71IjoyutKnLp5kYRT0APXHwH9W9Ah83yUSfS2egbfxOutpj7KpFbQ2zFqaEWnwJ7jZu0JDhwif_BUwWRDL1mMi09LAQUF1yqZ4eLqZvY5R4dRa8g8BeXKnn602ti-DmImdzHVskktCTqXdvE1OPfbwCTJriTtnw-m_fefmJ_pwuSTUPBE